BEGIN -- SET NOCOUNT ON added to prevent extra result sets from -- interfering with SELECT statements.
-- Insert statements for procedure here if @asset = 'accommodation' SELECT sum(acc.cost) total from Accommodation acc where acc.project_id = @projId if @asset ='telephone' SELECT sum(tel.cost) from Telephone tel where tel.project_id = @projId if @asset = 'employee' SELECT sum(acc.cost) from Employees acc where acc.project_id = @projId if @asset ='print' SELECT sum(tel.cost) from PrintMaterial tel where tel.project_id = @projId if @asset = 'refreshment' SELECT sum(acc.cost) from Refreshment acc where acc.project_id = @projId if @asset ='vehicle' SELECT sum(tel.cost) from Vehicle tel where tel.project_id = @projId if @asset ='wifi' SELECT sum(tel.cost) from Wifi tel where tel.project_id = @projId
END
